bangudesc:
la sutysisku is a fast dictionary for the Láadan language.

- Can I use it if I lose internet access?
- Yes, if this happens try opening this very address from this browser.
It should still open. A latest version of Chrome, Safari or Firefox is required.

For more resources visit Lojban Wiki.
title: Láadan dictionary la sutysisku
siskudescr: Search the Láadan dictionary la sutysisku.
opdescr: A dictionary for Láadan, Lojban, English and other languages that can work offline.
